ShoppingList

Shopping list provides infrastructure and functionality to handle multiple shopping lists for a customer account as well as manage shopping list items. A customer has a default shopping list, which will be created first time when there is a request made to manage its items. There is only one shopping list per customer by default, however one customer can have multiple named shopping lists, if required. The Shopping list is permanent and persists between sessions. Shopping list can be shared with other company users from the same business unit or with complete business units from the same company as the shopping list owner is assigned to.

 

Latest version: 2.7.0 View on GitHub
Last update: 10 Apr 2019
 
  Type: Core Splitted
Group: <none>

API (Facades)

Facade Method Description
createShoppingList

  • Create new shopping list entity if it does not exist.

  • Add create shopping list success message.
updateShoppingList

  • Update shopping list entity if it exist or create new.
removeShoppingList

  • Remove all items related to shipping list.

  • Remove all shared with company user relations of shopping list.

  • Remove all shared with company business unit relations of shopping list.

  • Remove shopping list.

  • Executes ShoppingListEvents::SHOPPING_LIST_UNPUBLISH event after removing.
clearShoppingList

  • Remove all shopping list items.
addItem

  • Adds item to shopping list.

  • Adds create shopping list success message if shopping list created.

  • Fails and adds error message when quantity is lesser equal than zero.
addItems

  • Adds items to the shopping list in persistence.

  • Adds success and failed messages through messenger facade.
removeItemById

  • Remove item by id.
getShoppingList

  • Load shopping list by id.
getShoppingListOverview

  • Get shopping list detail information.
getCustomerShoppingListCollection

  • Get shopping list collection by customer.

  • Shopping lists blacklisted for customer will be hidden.
getShoppingListItemCollection

  • Get items collection for shopping list collection.
getShoppingListItemCollectionTransfer

  • Get shopping list item collection by ids.
updateShoppingListItem

  • Update shopping list item.
createShoppingListFromQuote

  • Finds shopping list by id if exists.

  • Finds or creates shopping list by name if shopping list id absent.

  • Push items from quote to shopping list.
installShoppingListPermissions

  • Install shopping list permissions.
getShoppingListPermissionGroups

  • Get shopping list permission groups.
shareShoppingListWithCompanyBusinessUnit

  • Share shopping list with company business unit.
shareShoppingListWithCompanyUser

  • Share shopping list with company user.
updateShoppingListSharedEntities

  • Updates share shopping list with company business units and company users.
findCompanyUserPermissions

  • Finds company user shopping list permissions.
unShareShoppingListWithCompanyBusinessUnit

  • Remove company business unit from shared shopping list.
unShareCompanyUserShoppingLists

  • Remove company user relation from shared shopping lists.
dismissShoppingListSharing

  • Removes shopping list to company user relation if exists.

  • Adds shopping list to company user blacklist if company user business unit has access to shopping list.

  • Returns success if at least one action was executed.

Clients

Client Method Description
createShoppingList

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Create new shopping list entity if it does not exist.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Update shopping list entity if it exist or create new.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Remove all shopping list items.

  • Get messages from Zed request and put them to session.
addItem

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Hydrates ShoppingListItem with provided optional params.

  • Add item to shopping list.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.
addItems

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Add items to shopping list.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.
removeItemById

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Remove item by id.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.
getShoppingList

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Load shopping list by id.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.
getShoppingListOverviewWithoutProductDetails

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Create new shopping list entity if it does not exist.

  • Updates customer permissions.
getShoppingListOverview

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Get shopping list detail information.

  • Updates customer permissions.
getCustomerShoppingListCollection

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Get shopping list collection by customer.
addItemCollectionToCart

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Add shopping list items to cart.
getShoppingListItemCollection

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Get items collection for shopping list collection.

  • Updates customer permissions.
getShoppingListItemCollectionTransfer

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Get shopping list item collection by ids.

  • Updates customer permissions.
updateShoppingListItem

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Update shopping list item.

  • Updates customer permissions.
createShoppingListFromQuote

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Push items from quote to shopping list.

  • Updates customer permissions.

  • Get messages from zed request and put them to session.
getShoppingListPermissionGroups

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Get shopping list permission groups.
shareShoppingList

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Share shopping list with company users from business unit or exact company user.

  • Updates customer permissions.
updateShoppingListSharedEntities

  • Makes Zed request.

  • Updates share shopping list with company users from business unit or exact company user.
dismissShoppingListSharing

  • Makes zed request.

  • Removes shopping list to company user relation if exists.

  • Adds shopping list to company user blacklist if company user business unit has access to shopping list.

  • Returns success if at least one action was executed.

  • Updates customer permissions.
updateCustomerPermission

  • Gets customer from session.

  • Makes Zed request. Gets customer by email.

  • Updates customer in session.
calculateShoppingListSubtotal

  • Requires ProductViewTransfer::CurrentProductPrice.

  • Returns calculated subtotal.
